This folder contains all code for chapter 5 in our thesis.

All experiments are performed in R.

Start by loading "BCB.Rproj"

The folder "R" contains our custom built functions for this chapter.

The folder "Scripts" contains the R script used to provide the intuition behind persistent homology in R, and to conduct persistent homology in Python (which may be more feasible than in R, and allows to identify representative cycles).

The folder "Data" contains the data used in this chapter.

The folder "Experiments" contains the R scripts used to produce the results in Chapter 5.
